{"name":"Encouraging Words","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/feats/feats.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The target ally lost Stamina Points within the last round.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You give an ally within 30 feet a quick pep talk, helping them recover. Attempt a&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">@Check[type:diplomacy|dc:15|immutable:true]{Trained} </span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">Diplomacy check to grant the ally 5 Temporary Hit Points for 1 minute. The GM might adjust the DC based on the circumstances. If you have a sufficiently high proficiency in Diplomacy, you can instead attempt a </span>@Check[type:diplomacy|dc:20|immutable:true]{Expert}<span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"> check to increase the Temporary Hit Points gained by 10; a&nbsp;</span>@Check[type:diplomacy|dc:30|immutable:true]{Master}<span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"> check to increase the Temporary Hit Points by 30; or a&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">@Check[type:diplomacy|dc:40|immutable:true]{Legendary}</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">&nbsp;check to increase the Hit Points by 50. No matter the result, the ally is temporarily immune to Encouraging Words until for rest for the day.</span></p>\n<p>On a critical success, the ally is granted 5 additional Temporary Hit Points.</p>\n<hr style=\"border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-light-primary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light-highlight);\" />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong>&nbsp;The ally gains @compendium[EncouragingWordsRemake.encouraging-words-remake.Vgwp4fDZENPZO56b]{Critical Encouragement}.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The ally gains @compendium[EncouragingWordsRemake.encouraging-words-remake.UTcNvw2pq7DOAuR4]{Encouragement}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The ally becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 1}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Pathfinder Gamemastery Guide"},"traits":{"value":["auditory","general","linguistic","mental","skill","stamina"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":"encouraging-words","schema":{"version":0.743,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":2},"featType":{"value":"skill"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"trained in Diplomacy"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"1Cr1OR9d0oZ9xuA1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.dUnT3HWMFD3d2eBJ"}},"_id":"zRKHa72a97dGgVpp"}
